ActCanada Consumer Product Safety Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Schedule 1 to the Canada Consumer Product Safety Act (Treated Articles)
PrecisRegulations Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADA CONSUMER PRODUCT SAFETY ACT (TREATED ARTICLES) in order to modify item 6 of the Schedule to ensure that Act and Pest Control Products Act apply to consumer products that treated with a pesticide.
